## Unit 7: Reported Speech (Yes/No Questions)

### Bài 1: Chuyển câu hỏi Yes/No sang câu gián tiếp

1. "Do you speak English?" → He asked me if I spoke English.  
2. "Are you feeling better today?" → The doctor asked me if I was feeling better that day.  
3. "Did you watch the match last night?" → My friend asked me if I had watched the match the night before/the previous night.  
   "Will you come to my party?" → She asked me if I would come to her party .  
4. "Have you finished your homework?" → My mother asked me if I had finished my homework.  
5. "Can you swim?" → He asked me if I could swim.  
6. "Is it raining outside?" → She asked me if it was raining outside.  
7. "Did you enjoy the concert?" → They asked me if I enjoyed/had enjoyed the concert.  
8. "Have you ever been to Paris?" → He asked me if I had ever been to Paris.  
9. "Are you going to attend the meeting?" → My boss asked me if I was going to attend the meeting..

### Bài 2: Viết lại câu hỏi ở dạng gián tiếp

1. "Do you like chocolate?" Tom asked Mary.  
     
   Tom asked Mary if she liked chocolate.   
     
2. "Are you coming to the party?" She asked me.  
     
   She asked me if I was coming to the party.   
     
3. "Did you finish reading the book?" The teacher asked the student.  
     
   The teacher asked the student if she had finished reading the book.  
     
4. "Have you seen my keys?" My father asked.  
     
   My father asked me if I had seen his keys.  
     
5. "Will you help me with this project?" My colleague asked me.

 My colleague asked me if I would help her with that project.

### Bài 3: Hoàn thành câu với liên từ chỉ lý do (because, since, as, due to, because of)
